text: Peter Heli (born 27 February 1969) is an Estonian skier and floorball player. He competed in the Nordic combined event at the 1992 Winter Olympics. Heli placed 11th in floorball at the 1996 World Championships. ==References== Category:1969 births Category:Living people Category:Estonian male Nordic combined skiers Category:Olympic Nordic combined skiers of Estonia Category:Nordic combined skiers at the 1992 Winter Olympics Category:Estonian male biathletes Category:Sportspeople from Tallinn
